 * `node--[type]--search-result.html.twig`.
 *
 * The highlighted snippet comes from Search API's `search_api_excerpt` field
 * (added to the search_result view mode's view display config per content
 * type).
 */
#}
{{ include('citizen_sdc:node-search-result-base', {
